%h1= "#{@competition} - Heat Assignment"

%table.competitor_statuses.sortable
  %caption Competitors
  %thead
    %tr
      %th Heat
      %th.sign_up ID
      %th.sign_up Name
      %th.sign_up Age
      %th.sign_up Gender
      %th Age Group
      %th Best Time
      %th Geared
      %th Wheel Size
      %th Crank Size (mm)
      %th Notes
  %tbody
    - @competitors.each do |competitor|
      %tr
        %th= competitor.heat
        %td= competitor.lowest_member_bib_number
        %td= competitor.to_s
        %td= competitor.age
        %td= competitor.gender
        %td= competitor.age_group_entry_description
        %td= competitor.best_time
        %td= competitor.geared
        %td= competitor.riding_wheel_size
        %td= competitor.riding_crank_size
        %td= competitor.notes
%br

Upload a Spreadsheet containing 2 columns. ID and Heat. (no header row).
%br
Each row must contain a valid Registrant ID and Heat.

= form_tag upload_competition_heats_path(@competition), method: :post, :multipart=>true do
  = file_field_tag :file
  = submit_tag "Upload Heat assignments"

= link_to "Back", @competition
